Package: ProteoMaker
Type: Package
Title: Simulations of LC-MS Data from Proteoforms
Version: 0.6.19
Date: 2024-07-30
Author: Veit Schw√§mmle, Marie Locard-Paulet
Maintainer: Your Name <veits@bmb.sdu.dk>
Description: ProteoMaker is a package designed to simulate proteomics data from liquid-chromatography experiments. 
    It provides functions for generating ground truth data, simulating proteoform abundances, and performing 
    enzymatic digestion, mass spectrometry (MS) runs, and data analysis. The package includes functionality to 
    install necessary dependencies, load main scripts, and run simulations with configurable parameters.
